{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "11e68d31-c990-43dc-bcd7-ca20d818aa37", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/11e68d31-c990-43dc-bcd7-ca20d818aa37@1.pkg/1772597499842/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597500192", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/11e68d31-c990-43dc-bcd7-ca20d818aa37@1.pkg/1772597499842/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597500192"}, "identifier": "11e68d31-c990-43dc-bcd7-ca20d818aa37", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>题目考察香港稳定繁荣的原因。</p>\n\n<p>①正确：在党中央的正确领导下，国安法落地实施，说明党中央坚持依法治国的基本方略。</p>\n\n<p>②正确：香港落实“爱港者治港”原则，体现“一国两制”方针的巨大优越性。</p>\n\n<p>③正确：国安法实施后，香港由乱转治，百姓安居乐业，经济逐步复苏，体现祖国支持香港融入国家发展大局。</p>\n\n<p>④不符合题意：题干没有涉及香港繁荣稳定的原因是香港拥有高度自治权。</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（原创） 2025年7月1日是香港国安法实施5周年。5年前，香港虽经历风浪，但在党中央的正确领导下，国安法落地实施，落实“爱港者治港”原则，香港由乱转治，百姓安居乐业，经济逐步复苏，国家主权得到捍卫。由此可知，香港的稳定繁荣主要得益于（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①党中央坚持依法治国的基本方略</p>\n\n<p>②“一国两制”方针的巨大优越性</p>\n\n<p>③祖国支持香港融入国家发展大局</p>\n\n<p>④香港特别行政区拥有高度自治权</p>\n", "title": "（原创） 2025年7月1日是香港国安法实施5周年。5年前，香港虽经历风浪，但在党中央的正确领导下，国安法落地实施，落实“爱港者治港”原则，香港由乱转治，百姓安居乐业，经济逐步复苏，国家主权得到捍卫。由此可知，香港的稳定繁荣主要得益于（   ）①党中央坚持依法治国的基本方略②“一国两制”方针的巨大优越性③祖国支持香港融入国家发展大局④香港特别行政区拥有高度自治权", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/11e68d31-c990-43dc-bcd7-ca20d818aa37@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755182889178", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②③</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①③④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>②③④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（原创） 2025年7月1日是香港国安法实施5周年。5年前，香港虽经历风浪，但在党中央的正确领导下，国安法落地实施，落实“爱港者治港”原则，香港由乱转治，百姓安居乐业，经济逐步复苏，国家主权得到捍卫。由此可知，香港的稳定繁荣主要得益于（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①党中央坚持依法治国的基本方略</p>\n\n<p>②“一国两制”方针的巨大优越性</p>\n\n<p>③祖国支持香港融入国家发展大局</p>\n\n<p>④香港特别行政区拥有高度自治权</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "11e68d31